  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p><em><strong>Saving Face.</strong></em> Khil are careful not to show failure in front of their allies, for fear of being looked down on for slacking. If you miss with an attack roll or fail an ability check or a saving throw, you can gain a bonus to the roll equal to the number of allies you can see within 30 feet of you (maximum bonus of +5). Once you use this trait, you can’t use it again until you finish a short or long rest.</p>",
